PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FOne person has been killed and several
OL,8,Finjured after an Iranian drone attack
OL,9,Fstruck Kuwait International Airport,
OL,10,Fforcing the country to suspend all
OL,11,Fcommercial flights.
OL,13,FDefence Ministry spokesperson Saud
OL,14,FAbdulaziz Al-Otaibi said that "hostile
OL,15,Fdrones" had targeted Kuwait
OL,16,FInternational Airport's passenger
OL,17,Fbuilding on Wednesday, severely
OL,18,Fdamaging the structure and injuring "a
OL,19,Fnumber of individuals."
OL,26,@vD@_OUwD@GO]zD@eOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
