FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FThe attack comes just hours after Iran
OL,8,Fand the US exchanged missile strikes
OL,9,Fin the region, putting a strain on the
OL,10,Ffragile ceasefire.
OL,12,FThere were also reports that Iran had
OL,13,Fstopped communicating with mediators
OL,14,Fon Tuesday about extending a ceasefire
OL,15,Fin its war with the US and Israel.
OL,17,FUS President Donald Trump disputed the
OL,18,Freports and said negotiations were
OL,19,Fcontinuing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FOvernight, two Iranian missiles aimed
OL,8,Fat Kuwait broke apart during flight,
OL,9,Fwhile those targeting Bahrain were
OL,10,Fintercepted by US and Bahraini forces.
OL,12,FThe US Central Command said it
OL,13,Fresponded by striking an Iranian
OL,14,Fmilitary control station on Qeshm
OL,15,FIsland in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
