PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FIran's paramilitary Islamic
OL,8,FRevolutionary Guard Corps said it had
OL,9,Ftargeted the headquarters of the US
OL,10,FNavy's Fifth Fleet in Bahrain and
OL,11,Fanother country in the region during
OL,12,Fits attack, though it did not name
OL,13,FKuwait.
OL,15,FIt said the strikes were carried out
OL,16,Fin response to what it claimed was a
OL,17,FUS missile attack on the engine room
OL,18,Fof an oil tanker attempting to reach
OL,19,FIran despite the American blockade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"We had previously warned that in case
OL,8,Fof aggression, the response would be
OL,9,Fdifferent and more severe, and we
OL,10,Facted accordingly," the Guard said in
OL,11,Fits statement.
OL,13,FCentral Command also said it "downed
OL,14,Fmultiple drones" launched by Iran
OL,15,Ftargeting US forces in Kuwait.
OL,17,FTrump says talks 'going on
OL,18,Fcontinuously'
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
