FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Iran's Fars and Tasnim news
OL,8,Fagencies, both believed to be close to
OL,9,Fthe Guard, reported that Iran's
OL,10,Fnegotiators have stopped communicating
OL,11,Fwith ceasefire mediators as tensions
OL,12,Fflared in Israel's separate but
OL,13,Frelated fight against the Iranian-
OL,14,Fbacked Hezbollah militia in Lebanon.
OL,16,FHowever, Trump called reports of an
OL,17,Fend to talks "false and erroneous."
OL,26,@yD@NOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
