OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,F"The conversations between us have
OL,8,Fbeen going on continuously, including
OL,9,Ffour days ago, three days ago, two
OL,10,Fdays ago, one day ago and today,"
OL,11,FTrump said in a social media post.
OL,13,F"Where they lead, one never knows, but
OL,14,Fas I told Iran, 'It's time, one way or
OL,15,Fanother, for you to make a Deal."
OL,17,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio did
OL,18,Fnot address the reported cutoff in
OL,19,Ftalks as he testified at a
OL,20,Fcongressional hearing in Washington.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
