PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FInstead, he expressed optimism about
OL,8,Fthe nuclear aspect of the
OL,9,Fnegotiations, while warning that there
OL,10,Fis no guarantee of reaching "a deal
OL,11,Fthat's acceptable."
