PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FIran has been trying to increase
OL,8,Fpressure on Trump during negotiations
OL,9,Fover a ceasefire in the war, as well
OL,10,Fas over easing its control of the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz, through which oil,
OL,12,Fgas and other goods normally pass.
OL,14,FTrump could then press Israeli Prime
OL,15,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu to pause
OL,16,For slow the advance of Israeli forces,
OL,17,Fwhich have moved deeper into Lebanon
OL,18,Fthan at any point in more than 25
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780582265
OL,3,CIranian drone attack kills one in
OL,4,CKuwait as US and Iran launch new
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FThe conflicts have become increasingly
OL,8,Flinked, with Iran insisting that any
OL,9,Fceasefire must also include an end to
OL,10,Ffighting in Lebanon.
OL,12,FHowever, Israel and the US say the
OL,13,FLebanon fighting is separate from the
OL,14,Fceasefire negotiations over the Iran
OL,15,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
